title: I Went On International TV To Find A Stock Photo Model | Ep. 2
description: In this video, Max Fosh goes on a mission to find a stock photo model by appearing on international TV shows. He sets out to become a recognizable face in the stock photo world.
summary: Max Fosh goes to extreme lengths to become a stock photo model by appearing on international TV shows.
payoff: The payoff comes when Max successfully secures a spot in a stock photo agency by appearing on various TV shows, showcasing his dedication and commitment to the mission.
